_description: Description of the city of Rome — 70 lines in couplets

PROSC69565.First Lines:
ffro this worlde be gynyngvnto þat cyte of rome
                    makyng…
PROSC69565.Last Lines:
…And in transtiuer þat cuntrether in be stronge
                    ȝates thre…
